7 EQUIPMENT AND THE RIGHT TO REPAIR; CREATING THE MONTANA AGRICULTURAL EQUIPMENT
8 REPAIR BILL OF RIGHTS ACT; PROVIDING DEFINITIONS; APPLYING THE ACT TO AGRICULTURAL
9 EQUIPMENT MANUFACTURERS; PROVIDING EXCEPTIONS; AND PROVIDING A DELAYED EFFECTIVE
